data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Before plunge select right side missions (1) by pressing right button once.
Make ramps (2) until mode "Queens nest" (3) is lit.
Bash queen (4) five times and then start the mode in VUK (5).
Immediatelly bash queen (6) until multiball.
During multiball try shooting loops (7) to get bumper hits. The more bumper hits the better.
